arks the entry into the Mac market of MRP, which also makes theIBM PC-based Adman and Media Management Plus packages for advertising and PRagencies.andM;The program requires 2 Mbytes of RAM and a hard disk.andM;Marketing Resources Plus is at 151 N. Delaware, Suite 1750, Indianapolis,Ind.andP;  46207.andP;  Phone (317) 321-2600 or (800) 759-0181; fax (317) 321-2637.andO;</TEXT></DOC>